ar likelihood with $Planck$ breaks the\n$\\sigma_8$-$\\Omega_{\\rm m}$-degeneracy and yields $\\sigma_8=0.818 \\pm 0.013$\nand $\\Omega_{\\rm m} = 0.300 \\pm 0.011$ which is fully consistent with results\nfrom $Planck$ alone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2015 13:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2015 03:25:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-25"}
