 AWs and\nSMWs at kinetic scales, are taking place to jointly heat the protons\nperpendicularly and parallel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2015 13:11:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-11"}
