 predicted to be a very promising\ncandidate solar heating barrier material. The present work gives insight to the\nrole of A elements on the mechanical, superconducting and optical properties of\nNb4AC3 phases, and the obtained tendency by changing A elements will fertilize\nthe desirable materials design of functional ceramics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2015 14:17:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-15"}
